&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;We are seeking an&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Enterprise Application Support Engineer&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;to support and&amp;nbsp;maintain&amp;nbsp;a highly customized IBM Maximo environment and its supporting integration components within a mission-critical enterprise environment. This role focuses primarily on application sustainment, troubleshooting, integration support, patching, configuration, and operational support activities.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;The environment includes complex customizations, Java Server Pages (JSPs) Linux shell scripts, middleware configurations, and integrations with external workforce and enterprise systems. The selected candidate will work closely with developers, system administrators, database personnel, and customer stakeholders to&amp;nbsp;maintain&amp;nbsp;system stability, resolve technical issues, and support ongoing sustainment and modernization efforts.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
